<servinfosub id = "AFRAP70A9B06011003">
<title>
Repose 
</title>
<attention3>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Avant toute soudure, vérifier la position et la condition de pose de la pièce/des pièces de pose. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AFRAP70A9B04008"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
 / 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AFRAP70A9B04006"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
 / 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AFRAP70A9B04007"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Effectuer la réparation en tenant compte de la pose des pièces qui affectent l&#39;apparence. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AFRAP70A9B04003"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</attention3>
